# Visual-regression test failure captures
# Playwright writes <name>.actual.png beside the baseline <name>.png on diff
# failure (see packages/dashboard/tests/browser/capabilities-singleton-visual.test.ts).
# These are inspection artifacts, not source of truth — pollute the changelog
# every test run when the diff fails. Baselines (without .actual) stay tracked.
**/*.actual.png
